```plantuml
@startuml jlhood_retweet-leaderboard

actor User
entity "API Gateway" as APIGateway
entity "TweetProcessor Lambda" as TweetProcessorLambda
entity "GetLeaderboard Lambda" as GetLeaderboardLambda
entity "DynamoDB Leaderboard Table" as DynamoDB

User -> APIGateway: Request Leaderboard with optional 'limit'
APIGateway -> GetLeaderboardLambda: Invoke GetLeaderboard
GetLeaderboardLambda -> DynamoDB: Query leaderboard data
DynamoDB --> GetLeaderboardLambda: Return leaderboard data
GetLeaderboardLambda --> APIGateway: Return formatted leaderboard data
APIGateway --> User: Display leaderboard

note right of User: User views leaderboard

== Tweet Processing Flow ==

entity "Twitter Event Source" as Twitter

Twitter -> TweetProcessorLambda: Trigger with tweet JSON
TweetProcessorLambda -> TweetProcessorLambda: Parse tweet JSON
TweetProcessorLambda -> TweetProcessorLambda: Filter tweet (not native retweet, at least 1 retweet)
TweetProcessorLambda -> DynamoDB: Update leaderboard with retweet count
DynamoDB --> TweetProcessorLambda: Acknowledge update

@enduml
```